data.description: Charming and secluded, this enchanting property at 427980 County Rd., 65 in Loxley, Alabama offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Nestled in a serene countryside setting, this home provides a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. Boasting a spacious floor plan, the residence features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with 3000 sq ft. of living space. Natural light floods the living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere. The property also offers a very large corner lot (one acre) With its generous acreage, there is ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the picturesque surroundings. Conveniently located in Loxley, residents can easily access nearby amenities, schools, and recreational areas. This property presents a unique opportunity to own a slice of serenity in the heart of Alabama's beautiful countryside. Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and allure of 427980 County Road 65. A new AC was installed in December of 2023. The sellers will provide the buyers with a one-year home warranty.
